{"tid":1428105,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［推］［要人！！］8．8 史學界集會","createTime":"2019-08-07T08:51:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T11:39:39.000Z","uid":192678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1454e185e229d4b21491ce4e29fc1b4781fb4620","tid":1428105,"uid":192678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:51:27.000Z","msg":"歡迎所有熱愛歷史嘅人參與，推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「洞鑒古今守良知 徹查真相護我城」8&middot;8 史學界集會<br />\n<br />\n****************<br />\n<br />\n「人與政權的鬥爭，就是記憶與遺忘的鬥爭。」&mdash;&mdash; 米蘭&middot;昆德拉<br />\n<br />\n我們是一群中大歷史系學生。<br />\n自政府在三月將《逃犯及刑事事宜相互法律協助法例（修訂）條例草案》提交立法會起，反對修例的運動至今已演變成關於五大訴求的社會運動。史學研究的核心思想為求真，作為歷史人，我們應當提倡成立獨立調查委員會，就事態的來龍去脈尋求真相，為運動期間的各種不公討回公道。故此，我們將舉辦一個歷史人集會，向外界宣傳五大訴求及表明歷史人的立場。我們誠邀您參與是次集會，活動詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n活動名稱：「洞鑒古今守良知 徹查真相護我城」集會<br />\n舉行日期：八月八日（星期四）<br />\n舉行時間：下午六時<br />\n舉行地點：香港中文大學新亞書院圓形廣場<br />\n舉行對象：任何歷史界別/對歷史有興趣的人士<br />\n集會內容：一、影片放映會；二、分享會；三、集思會 <br />\n交通路線：校巴2號線前往新亞書院/晚上七時後校巴N號線前往新亞書院<br />\n嘉賓（按筆劃排序，稍後或有更新）：<br />\n朱福強教授（政府檔案處前處長，香港中文大學歷史系客席副教授）<br />\n馬木池博士（香港中文大學歷史系講師）<br />\n潘毅教授（香港大學社會學系教授、香港中文大學歷史系校友）<br />\n<br />\n在集思會環節，任何參加者皆可以上台發表講話，內容不限，但建議以成立獨立調查委員會為題。如任何史學界人士需要大會司儀代為發言，請以google form遞交您的意見。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle form 網址：<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSciDP22QzWQarxbMJgNAXMfzT-MQC0rYkgOqcTDh_GL6xZu3w/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSciDP22QzWQarxbMJgNAXMfzT-MQC0rYkgOqcTDh_GL6xZu3w%2Fviewform&d=%2BDaDB54%2FKEfuO7Vsi8VjQ17Oh%2FyAFRgp1rU3tL1w%2BGY%3D&h=f5e15262\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSciDP22QzWQarxbMJgNAXMfzT-MQC0rYkgOqcTDh_GL6xZu3w/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\n雨程安排：舉行地點轉為康本國際學術園二樓LT7<br />\n<br />\n如有需要，可透過電郵 cuhkhistseekthetruth@gmail.com 聯絡我們。<br />\n<br />\n我們再次呼籲各位撥冗出席是次集會。在這漫長的黑夜裏，守護黎明的降臨。歷史人，一同編寫歷史！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/488698118547832/?ti=icl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F488698118547832%2F%3Fti%3Dicl&d=%2BDaDB54%2FKEfuO7Vsi8VjQ17Oh%2FyAFRgp1rU3tL1w%2BGY%3D&h=389d2eb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/488698118547832/?ti=icl</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/huyaASM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhuyaASM.png&h=90fad6c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f16151a351bd6a621013c9f9f1c0fc5c3375dba5","tid":1428105,"uid":192678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:53:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32d5a487a05618af2fc722468d24c8edbbff6fc2","tid":1428105,"uid":192678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:53:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3130bd65226ebe1c43809fd117e17be49244dc4","tid":1428105,"uid":192678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:04:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0f9ef46b5d30e63bc673fee5563f10644d5410d","tid":1428105,"uid":192678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:05:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3e7b206e00b531ed20aedcb2f6eeeded46b1aeb","tid":1428105,"uid":192678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:39:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img